    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to furniture or built-in features in the form of an upright partition that can be used to embellish, partition, shelter, and provide privacy. Screens are often highly decorated.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
